    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a dependable choice for daily driving. While the exterior shows some minor surface scratches and the interior has light wear on the driver's seat, the car is clean, smoke-free, and mechanically sound. It\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a slipping transmission and an engine that requires a major overhaul to be reliable. The exterior shows its age with several large dents, rusted panels, and failing clear coat, while the interior has heavy staining and multiple tears in the upholstery. This car would be best suited for a dedicated mechanic looking for a project or as a donor vehicle for parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this showroom-condition masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and presenting in absolute mint condition, this vehicle offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the pre-owned market. Fully inspected and ready for the discerning owner who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You know how much I love my cars, and it honestly breaks my heart a little to let this one go. This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed with nothing but the best products. It truly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor; the paint is gleaming and the interior still has that wonderful new-car scent. I\u2019ve kept up with every single service, no matter how small, because I believe a car this special deserves to be treated right. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s as close to perfect as it gets, you\u2019ve found it. Why not swing by, grab a coffee, and see why I\u2019m so head-over-heels for this car?",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a museum-quality E46 M3, a true benchmark of the S54 platform. This example features a surgically precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox mated to a high-revving inline-six that pulls with relentless linearity. The critical subframe reinforcement has been completed using a bespoke plate kit, ensuring structural integrity far beyond OEM specifications. The VANOS system has been fully bulletproofed with Beisan components, resulting in razor-sharp throttle response and a whisper-quiet idle. Suspended on a perfectly corner-balanced set of Bilstein B16 adjustable coilovers, the turn-in is telepathic. Preventative rod bearing replacement was performed as a precaution, not a necessity, ensuring this powerplant is ready for the next 100k miles. The finish is deep and lustrous, and the Nappa leather interior remains supple and unmarked. This is an analog masterpiece for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Performance ready. Lowest price for this condition. Buy it now or someone else will.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine sliding into a cockpit that smells of heritage and fine leather, where every stitch tells a story of unparalleled craftsmanship. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a rolling masterpiece, a symphony of polished chrome and deep, lustrous paint that catches the light like a mirror. When you turn the key, the engine doesn't just start\u2014it awakens with a purposeful, rhythmic hum that promises endless horizons and the kind of effortless grace that modern machines have long forgotten. This is a rare invitation to own a piece of automotive poetry, preserved in a state that truly defies the passage of time. To drive it is to step into a dream where the road never ends and the world stands still in admiration.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the standard for 'mint' condition. This specimen has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless factory finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. With a comprehensive service history and meticulous attention to every mechanical detail, this car represents a rare opportunity for the collector who demands absolute perfection. Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence in a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    }
  ],
